    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It drives smoothly and I've made sure to keep up with it so it's ready for its next adventure! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great pulling into the driveway, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32400.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
