      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders, with the critical VANOS system recently serviced using Beisan seals and a cryo-treated exhaust hub. The chassis has been structurally addressed with a subframe reinforcement kit and upgraded Powerflex bushings to eliminate rear-end deflection. Performance is further sharpened by a set of Bilstein B6 dampers and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synergy and throttle response remain exceptionally crisp.",
